author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Electrical wire sealing tips…I have a bunch of penetrations in the bottom plates for electrical wires. So I use @greatstufffoam Fireblock to seal them. This impedes the spread of smoke and flames in case there’s a fire in an adjacent room. Plus the smart dispenser allows this can to be used for up to 30 days, which is nice while I’m working on the entire bathroom remodel. Many thanks to Great Stuff for sponsoring this tutorial 🔥#electrical #greatstufffoam #bathroomremodel #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
